e making\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an honor to be able to do that,\\\" said Ann.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an honor\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"Ann\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ann's Olympic dreams were almost over before they started when he was shot in the leg in Minneapolis last November.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minneapolis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.667604006034062e-14, \"text\": \"Minneapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minneapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minneapolis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ann's Olympic dreams\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"the leg\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He spent several weeks in the hospital recovering, but he was eventually strong enough to travel to Senegal for qualifications.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several weeks\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the hospital recovering\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"Senegal\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifications\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was scary.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You train so hard for something and it can be taken away just like that,\\\" said Ann.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"Ann\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ann hopes to become a flag bearer at the Summer Games, but bringing home an Olympic medal for taekwondo would be a real kick.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"n